Intrinsicality	#5.	 invariable, incurable, incorrigible, ineradicable, fixed. intrinsically &c. adj.
Obstinacy	#606.	 incorrigible, deaf to advice, impervious to reason
Disobedience	#742.	 breachy, insubordinate, impatient of control, incorrigible
Hopelessness	#859.	 incorrigible
Vice	#945.	 sunk in iniquity, lost in iniquity, steeped in iniquity. incorrigible, irreclaimable, obdurate, reprobate, past praying for
Impenitence	#951.	 relentless, remorseless, graceless, shriftless. lost, incorrigible, irreclaimable. unreconstructed, unregenerate, unreformed
